## Controversies and Alternatives
Some editors argue that excessive redirects create maintenance overhead. The [Wikipedia:Redirects for discussion](/Wikipedia:Redirects_for_discussion) process addresses contentious cases. Automated tools like [WP:AWB](/Wikipedia:AutoWikiBrowser) help manage redirect networks efficiently.

